CVE-2018-15919.summary: Remotely observable behaviour in auth-gss2.c in OpenSSH through 7.8 could be used by remote attackers to detect existence of users on a target system when GSS2 is in use. NOTE: the discoverer states 'We understand that the OpenSSH developers do not want to treat such a username enumeration (or "oracle") as a vulnerability.'

CVE-2017-15906.summary: The process_open function in sftp-server.c in OpenSSH before 7.6 does not properly prevent write operations in readonly mode, which allows attackers to create zero-length files.

English version

HECTOR FIORE

Una version mía de "Because" de J. Lennon para flauta y medios electrónicos interactivos

because


Mi tema "Accents" para computadora, clarinete electrónico y percusión (7.00 Min.)

accents

"Las vaquitas son ajenas" on a CD by "Muzyka Centrum"


I have already performed my works at different festivals and concerts in Europe, Americas and Asia:

Peking,CHINA: Tsinghua University Auditorium; International Computer Music Conference - ICMC 99. World first performance of his piece "Son sin marimba" for percussion & electronics. Krakow, POLONIA: He has participated as a composer and as a performer in many editions of the international Festival "Musique dans le vieux Cracovie". Budapest, HUNGRIA: He has played his music at the REPRISE, Az Ear Egyuttes Hangversenyei - Az Uj Szinhaz Studioszinpadan. Vilnius, LITHUANIA: Mokytoju namai - Krokuvos Kulturos Dienos Vilniuje; playing with the "Muzyka Centrum Ensemble". Zamosc,POLONIA: Concerts with the "Peripeties Improvisation Duo" at the Art of Improvising 2000 International Festival - Trans Sztuki Nowa Era Duch Instytut Sztuki Nowej. Ljubljana, SLOVENIA: Municipal Gallery; Solo concerts at the "Winter Salon\'99". Vienna, AUSTRIA: Italienisches Kulturinstitut, Grosser Saal, solo concerts at the "Eroffnung der Ausstellung CONTRORITMO der Kunstlerinnengruppe OSMOSI". Cracow, POLAND: Goethe Institut, world first performance of is piece "Eclosion". In addition, he has played solo concerts and world first performances in many editions of the International Summer Workshops for New Music Krakow/Stuttgart. He has played at the most important concert halls in the city too. Copenhagen, DENMARK: D.I.E.M.; Danish Film Institute and Denmark\'s National Radio; his music has been played at the Cinema for de Ear, Spatial Sonic Art at Cinemateket.  B. Klodzka, POLAND:Municipal Concert Hall, solo concerts and first performances in many editions of the Polish Master Courses of Contemporary Music Interpretation. BsAs., ARGENTINA: He has played many times at the Centro Cultural Ciudad de Bs.As. (CCCBA); Centro Cultural Ricardo Rojas (UBA). Also at the "El Cubo" Theatre, on the "Cambalache" International Tango Festival. Warsaw, POLAND: Artistic director of the Argentinean Embassy First Cycle of Concerts of Argentinean Contemporary Music in Poland. La Plata, ARGENTINA: Centro de las Artes Teatro Argentino at many editions of the "Encuentro Internacional de Produccion Artistica en Formato Digital" UNLP - FBA. Swidnica, POLONIA: World first performance of his pieces "Bijcie dzwony" & "Oye mi piano!"  Cracow, POLONIA: Hector Fiore (PSeME) at the "Festiwal Audio Art’08". Mendoza, ARGENTINA: Concert of piccolo music by Hector Fiore at the "I World Flute Festival 2009".

hector@fiore.art.pl

Hector Fiore

"Karawana" para flauta, medios electrónicos interactivos y percusion:

karawana



I play flute, live electronics media and computers in different stages in Europe and America, performing my own projects or other composers works.

The great majority of my pieces have already been performed at different festivals and concerts in Europe, Americas and Asia. Some of them have been representing Poland or Argentina at international events.
